<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?xml-stylesheet href="/rss-styles.xsl" type="text/xsl"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Fiky Baharudin</title><description>A DevOps Engineer, Programmer and Hobbyist</description><link>https://porto.fikyb.my.id/</link><item><title>Integrating Cloudflare R2 with Laravel and Custom Domain</title><link>https://porto.fikyb.my.id/post/cloudflare-r2-laravel-custom-domain/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://porto.fikyb.my.id/post/cloudflare-r2-laravel-custom-domain/</guid><description>How to set up Cloudflare R2 as Laravel&apos;s filesystem using the S3 driver, with a custom domain for public file access.</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;Cloudflare R2 is an object storage service compatible with the Amazon S3 API. Because of this, Laravel can access R2 using the built-in &lt;code&gt;s3&lt;/code&gt; driver through Flysystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bucket: &lt;code&gt;my-app-assets&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Custom domain: &lt;code&gt;assets.example.com&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Domain and bucket names have been anonymized.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;1-install-the-s3-adapter&quot;&gt;1. Install the S3 Adapter&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Run:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt;composer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt; require&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt; league/flysystem-aws-s3-v3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;2-create-an-r2-api-token&quot;&gt;2. Create an R2 API Token&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Go to the Cloudflare Dashboard:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2 Object Storage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;→ Manage R2 API Tokens&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;→ Create API Token&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grant &lt;code&gt;Object Read &amp;#x26; Write&lt;/code&gt; permissions, preferably scoped to the specific bucket being used.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Save the following information:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Access Key ID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Secret Access Key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Account ID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Bucket Name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Never store these credentials directly in your repository.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;3-configure-the-laravel-environment&quot;&gt;3. Configure the Laravel Environment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add the following to your &lt;code&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt; file:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;plaintext&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;FILESYSTEM_DISK=r2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-access-key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-secret-key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_BUCKET=my-app-assets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_ENDPOINT=https://ACCOUNT_ID.r2.cloudflarestorage.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_URL=https://assets.example.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_REGION=auto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;R2 uses the &lt;code&gt;auto&lt;/code&gt; region. The value &lt;code&gt;us-east-1&lt;/code&gt; can also be used by applications that don’t support it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Important notes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;R2_ENDPOINT&lt;/code&gt; is used by Laravel to communicate with the R2 API.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;R2_URL&lt;/code&gt; is used to generate public URLs through the custom domain.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do not replace the API endpoint with the custom domain.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;4-add-the-r2-disk&quot;&gt;4. Add the R2 Disk&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Open &lt;code&gt;config/filesystems.php&lt;/code&gt; and add:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;php&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;disks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; [&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;r2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; [&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;driver&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;s3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt; env&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;secret&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt; env&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;region&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt; env&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;R2_REGION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;bucket&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt; env&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;R2_BUCKET&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;endpoint&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt; env&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;R2_ENDPOINT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;url&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt; env&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;R2_URL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;use_path_style_endpoint&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; false,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; true,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    ],&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;],&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then clear the configuration cache:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt; artisan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt; config:clear&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;5-upload-a-file&quot;&gt;5. Upload a File&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Example upload through a controller:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;php&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#F78C6C&quot;&gt;use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt; Illuminate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;Http&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;Request&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#F78C6C&quot;&gt;use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt; Illuminate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;Support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;Facades&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;Storage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C792EA&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C792EA&quot;&gt; function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt; upload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt;Request&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; $&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;request&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    $&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;request&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;-&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;validate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;([&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; [&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;required&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;max:10240&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;],&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    ]);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    $&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;path &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt; Storage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;disk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;r2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;)-&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;putFile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;uploads&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        $&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;request&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;-&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    );&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF;font-style:italic&quot;&gt;    return&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt; response&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;()-&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;([&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; $&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;        &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;url&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt; =&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt; Storage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;disk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;r2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;)-&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;url&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;($&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#EEFFFF&quot;&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    ]);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Resulting URL:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;https://assets.example.com/uploads/example.jpg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;6-connect-a-custom-domain&quot;&gt;6. Connect a Custom Domain&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the Cloudflare Dashboard:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;→ Select Bucket&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;→ Settings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;→ Custom Domains&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;→ Connect Domain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Example domain:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;assets.example.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The domain must be on a Cloudflare zone linked to the R2 account. A custom domain is recommended for production because it supports Cloudflare caching, WAF, access control, redirects, and analytics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;7-testing&quot;&gt;7. Testing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Upload a simple file through Laravel Tinker:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt; artisan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt; tinker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;php&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt;Storage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;disk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;r2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;)-&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;put&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;test.txt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;    &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;Hello from Laravel and Cloudflare R2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check the URL:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;php&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt;Storage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;disk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;r2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;)-&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#82AAFF&quot;&gt;url&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt;test.txt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#89DDFF&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expected result:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;https://assets.example.com/test.txt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;common-issues&quot;&gt;Common Issues&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;upload-succeeds-but-url-doesnt-use-the-custom-domain&quot;&gt;Upload succeeds but URL doesn’t use the custom domain&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make sure the following configuration is set:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;plaintext&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_URL=https://assets.example.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then run:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFCB6B&quot;&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt; artisan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C3E88D&quot;&gt; config:clear&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;custom-domain-is-accessible-but-upload-fails&quot;&gt;Custom domain is accessible but upload fails&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make sure &lt;code&gt;R2_ENDPOINT&lt;/code&gt; uses the API endpoint:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;plaintext&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_ENDPOINT=https://ACCOUNT_ID.r2.cloudflarestorage.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Not:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;plaintext&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;R2_ENDPOINT=https://assets.example.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;file-returns-http-404-or-403&quot;&gt;File returns HTTP 404 or 403&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check that:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The custom domain is active.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The file actually exists in the bucket.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The path and filename are correct.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The bucket is intended for public access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;presigned-urls-dont-work-through-the-custom-domain&quot;&gt;Presigned URLs don’t work through the custom domain&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;R2 presigned URLs only work using the S3 API domain:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;ACCOUNT_ID.r2.cloudflarestorage.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Presigned URLs cannot use a custom domain directly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;conclusion&quot;&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Integrating Laravel with Cloudflare R2 requires two different URLs:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;astro-code material-theme-darker&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#212121;color:#EEFFFF; overflow-x: auto;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;API endpoint → upload, delete, and storage operations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Custom domain → public file access&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Keeping these separate is important. Using the custom domain as the API endpoint is one of the most common reasons why R2 connections from Laravel fail.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded><updated/></item><item><title>This is my First Post</title><link>https://porto.fikyb.my.id/post/first-post/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://porto.fikyb.my.id/post/first-post/</guid><description>My First Blog using TinaCMS</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 11:05:19 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;Yeah, this is my first time using Astro+TinaCMS. i think it will hard because i don’t know much about Javascript but after a few days i look at documentation, tutorial and asking to AI (ChatGPT and Gemini) i think i know how it works.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;also thanks to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/cassidoo/blahg&quot;&gt;cassidoo &lt;/a&gt;for making this template so i can learn and use it for myself.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded><updated/></item></channel></rss>